WEBVTT

01:26:19.233 --> 01:26:21.024
of the very system that we live in

01:26:21.608 --> 01:26:22.608
and look up to.

01:26:22.774 --> 01:26:23.858
I hope you get the point.

01:26:25.441 --> 01:26:26.691
-Philip...
-Sir?

01:26:27.316 --> 01:26:29.399
Do you know Sahadevan
from the Varun case?

01:26:30.108 --> 01:26:31.524
I don't know him personally, sir.

01:26:31.899 --> 01:26:33.108
I've only heard of him.
